<h4 id="crud">CRUD:</h4>

<p>REST - –ø–µ—Ä–µ–¥–∞—á–∞ —Ä–µ–ø—Ä–µ–∑–µ–Ω—Ç–∞—Ç–∏–≤–Ω–æ–≥–æ —Å–æ—Å—Ç–æ—è–Ω–∏—è (–∞—Ä—Ö–∏—Ç–µ–∫—Ç—É—Ä–Ω—ã–π —Å—Ç–∏–ª—å —Ä–∞–∑—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∫–∏ —Ä–∞—Å–ø—Ä–µ–¥–µ–ª—ë–Ω–Ω—ã—Ö —Å–µ—Ç–µ–≤—ã—Ö —Å–∏—Å—Ç–µ–º). –†–æ–π –§–æ–ª–¥–∏–Ω–≥, 2000</p>

<ul>
  <li>C - POST - CREATE</li>
  <li>R - GET - READ</li>
  <li>U - PATCH - UPDATE</li>
  <li>D - DELETE - DESTROY</li>
</ul>

<p>–ú–∞—Ä—à—Ä—É—Ç—ã RESTful - CRUD - –æ–ø–µ—Ä–∞—Ü–∏–∏ –ë–î –∏ 4 –º–µ—Ç–æ–¥–∞ HTTP-–∑–∞–ø—Ä–æ—Å–∞ + link_to (–¥–ª—è —Å—Å—ã–ª–∫–∏)</p>

<ul>
  <li>index - /users - GET - users_path</li>
  <li>show - /users/1 - GET - user</li>
  <li>new - /users/new - GET - new_user_path</li>
  <li>edit - /users/1/edit - GET - edit_user_path(user)</li>
  <li>create - /users - POST</li>
  <li>update - /users/1 - PATCH</li>
  <li>destroy - /users/1 - DELETE - user, method: :delete</li>
</ul>

<p>–†–µ—à–∏—Ç—å, –∫–∞–∫–∏–µ –∫–æ–Ω—Ç—Ä–æ–ª–ª–µ—Ä—ã –∏ –º–µ—Ç–æ–¥—ã –Ω–µ–æ–±—Ö–æ–¥–∏–º—ã: —Å—Ç—Ä—É–∫—Ç—É—Ä. –ø—Ä–∏–ª–æ–∂–µ–Ω–∏–µ –∏—Å–ø–æ–ª—å–∑. —Ä–µ—Å—É—Ä—Å—ã –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–µ –º–æ–≥—É—Ç CRUD</p>

<p>controller:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">def</span> <span style="color:#06B;font-weight:bold">index</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  <span style="color:#33B">@users</span> = <span style="color:#036;font-weight:bold">User</span>.all
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>view:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>&lt;<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">% </span><span style="color:#D20">@users.each</span><span style="color:#710"> </span></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |user| <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%&gt;</span><span style="color:#D20"></span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#D20">  &lt;%= user.name %</span><span style="color:#710">&gt;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>  &lt;<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%=</span><span style="color:#D20"> user.email %&gt;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#D20"></span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#D20">  &lt;%</span><span style="color:#710">=</span></span> link_to <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">Show</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>, user <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%&gt;</span><span style="color:#D20"></span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#D20">  &lt;%= link_to 'Edit', edit_user_path(user) %</span><span style="color:#710">&gt;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>  &lt;<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%=</span><span style="color:#D20"> link_to 'Destroy', user, method: :delete %&gt;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#D20">&lt;% end %&gt;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#D20"></span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#D20">&lt;%</span><span style="color:#710">=</span></span> link_to <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">New User</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>, new_user_path <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%&gt;</span><span style="color:#D20"></span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#D20"></span></span></pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<h4 id="link_to">link_to</h4>

<ul>
  <li>users list - users_path</li>
  <li>show - user</li>
  <li>new user - new_user_path</li>
  <li>edit - edit_user_path(user)</li>
  <li>destroy - user, method: :delete</li>
</ul>

